quran[78]{c,v,t}:
  55,1,Ramehauhelo
  55,2,Ke Eena ea rutileng Qura’n
  55,3,U hlotse motho
  55,4,U mo rutile puo
  55,5,Letsatsi le ngoeli li latela tsela ea tsona
  55,6,Lihlahla le lifate – bobeli li ithapalatsa tlas’a Allah
  55,7,U phahamiselitse Leholimo holimo-limo; A ba a ts’epamisa molao
  55,8,Hore le tle le se ke la tlola molao
  55,9,Latelang molao ka hloko kantle le botloko-tsebe
  55,10,U batalalitse lefats’e molemong oa libopuoa tsa Hae
  55,11,Leo holim’a lona ho nang le litholoana le lifate tsa palema tse hlahisang litholoana
  55,12,Le lijo-thollo le tsona limela tse monko o monate
  55,13,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,14,U bopile motho ka letsopa joaloka liboptjoa tsa letsopa
  55,15,Lisabonoeng (li-jinn) U li bopile ka mollo o hlokang mosi
  55,16,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,17,"Ke Mong`a ‘nga tse peli tsa Bochabela, le Mong`a ‘nga tse peli tsa Bophirima"
  55,18,Ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang
  55,19,"Etsoe ke Eena ea lokolotseng maoatle a mabeli, hore a kopane"
  55,20,Ho teng moeli lipakeng tsa ona hoo ka bobeli ba ona oo a ke keng a o tlola
  55,21,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,22,Bobeling ba ona ho hlaha liperela le likhetla
  55,23,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,24,"Likepe tseo tse sesang holima leoatle, tse ts’oanang le lithaba ke tsa Hae"
  55,25,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,26,"Mang, kapa mang ea teng mona lefats’eng o tla shoa"
  55,27,"Ho tla sala feela ke boteng ba Mong`a hau, – Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tlotlehang"
  55,28,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,29,Lintho tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lifats’eng li kopa ho Eena. Ka mehla eohle U bonts’a matla a feletseng a Hae
  55,30,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,31,Haufi re tla fana ka qeto litabeng tsa mafats’e a lona bobeli
  55,32,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,33,"Oho lona ‘moka oa Masabonoeng le batho! Haeba le na le matla a ho tsamaea hohle libakeng tsa maholimo le lefats’e, etsang joalo! Ruri! Le ke ke la etsa joalo kantle le taelo ea Rona"
  55,34,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,35,"Khahlanong le lona ho tla romelloa lelakabe la mollo le mosi, le ke ke la phonyoha"
  55,36,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,37,"Mohla leholimo le petsohang ka lehare, le fetoha leba lefubelu ba setlolo –"
  55,38,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,39,Letsatsing leo motho esita le ea sa bonoeng (jinni) ba sa tlong ho botsoa ho latela libe tsa bona
  55,40,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,41,"Baetsalibe ba tla tsebahala ka mats’oao, ebile ba tla tutloa ka moriri le ka maoto"
  55,42,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,43,Sena ke lihele tseo Baetsalibe ba li latolang
  55,44,Ba tla ba loebaloeba metsing a belang
  55,45,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,46,"Empa haele mang, kapa mang ea ts’abang ho tjamela Mong`a hae mohla Letsatsi la kahlolo, ho tla ba teng Lirapa tse peli"
  55,47,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,48,Tse nang le mefuta eohle (ea lifate le limomonane)
  55,49,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,50,Har’a tsona ho na le liliba tse peli tse phallang
  55,51,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,52,Har’a tsona ho tla ba le mefuta eohle ea litholoana ka bobeli
  55,53,"Joale, ke molemo ofeng oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,54,"Kamoo, ba tla phomola holim’a mealo e aliloeng ka mekhahlelo e khabisitsoeng ka Selika, litholoana tsa Lirapa tseo ka bobeli li le haufi le matsoho a bona"
  55,55,"Joale, ke molemo ofe oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,56,"Kamoo ho teng basetsana ba hloekileng ba es’o kang ba angoa ke tse sa bonoeng (lijinni), kapa banna pele ho bona"
  55,57,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,58,Ba ts’oanang le majoe a lirubi le majoe a mefuta a leoatle ka botle
  55,59,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,60,Na moputso oa botle ha se botle
  55,61,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,62,"Kathoko ho lirapa tsena, ho teng lirapa tse ling tse peli"
  55,63,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,64,Tse makhasi a `mala o motala tlaka-tlaka
  55,65,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,66,Tse nang le liliba tse peli tse kopotsang kahosafeleng
  55,67,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,68,Tse nang le Litholoana le palema le likharenate ka hare ho tsona
  55,69,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,70,"Ho bile ho teng balekane ba lokileng, ba khahlehang, ba batle – –"
  55,71,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,72,"Balekane ba lihlong, ba luutseng likheleng tse lokileng –"
  55,73,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,74,Bao ho seng monna le ha e le tse sa bonoeng tse kileng tsa ba ama pele ho bona –
  55,75,"Joale, ke ofeng molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,76,Ba phomotseng holim’a mealo e metalana le eona meseme e khahlehang
  55,77,"Joale, ke ofe molemo oa melemo ea Mong`a lona oo le o latolang"
  55,78,"Lebitso la Mong`a hau le hlohonolofale, Ea Matla Oohle, Ea Tlotlehang"